OL,3,CDrink driver who killed grandmother in
OL,4,Chead-on crash jailed
OL,6,FA drink driver who killed a "beloved"
OL,7,Fmother and grandmother in a head-on
OL,8,Fcollision has been jailed.
OL,10,F65-year-old Linda Stockdale died when
OL,11,Fan Audi A7 hit her Kia as she was
OL,12,Freturning home to Tunstall after baby-
OL,13,Fsitting her grandchildren.
OL,15,FIt happened on the A6055 between
OL,16,FCatterick and Leeming Bar at around
OL,17,F2.18am on 1 August 2021.
OL,19,FLinda died at the scene.
