OL,3,CDrink driver who killed grandmother in
OL,4,Chead-on crash jailed
OL,6,FThe Audi's driver, 24-year-old Oliver
OL,7,FHartley from Leeds, had taken the car
OL,8,Ffrom his mother's home in Harrogate
OL,9,Fwithout her permission. He was not
OL,10,Finsured to drive it.
OL,12,FHe had also been drinking alcohol
OL,13,Fbefore driving on the wrong side of
OL,14,Fthe road.
OL,16,FHartley was awaiting trail for causing
OL,17,Fdeath by dangerous driver, However he
OL,18,Foffered a lesser plea of causing death
OL,19,Fby careless driving which was accepted.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
