OL,3,CDrink driver who killed grandmother in
OL,4,Chead-on crash jailed
OL,6,FHe was jailed for 12 months at York
OL,7,FCrown Court, banned from driving for
OL,8,Fsix months and will have to take an
OL,9,Fextended driving test.
OL,11,FDC Laura Cleary, of the Major
OL,12,FCollision Investigation Team, said
OL,13,FHartley showed an "appalling lack of
OL,14,Fconcern to the safety of other road
OL,15,Fusers."
OL,17,FFollowing his sentencing, Linda's son,
OL,18,FPhilip Stockdale said his mother was a
OL,19,F"kind, thoughtful, and caring" person.
