OL,4,Chead-on crash jailed
OL,6,F"Her loss has been devastating for so
OL,7,Fmany, not only family but many
OL,8,Flifelong friends, colleagues, and
OL,9,Fneighbours.
OL,11,F"It has been extremely difficult for
OL,12,Fme to put into words the impact of
OL,13,Flosing my mum as I simply don't think
OL,14,FI can do her justice."
OL,16,FHe added that his mother was just four
OL,17,Fdays away from retirement.
OL,19,FLinda's partner of 25 years,
OL,20,FChristopher Gall, was left with ill
OL,21,Fhealth after her death.
