OL,3,CDrink driver who killed grandmother in
OL,4,Chead-on crash jailed
OL,6,F"I have suffered with a blood clot in
OL,7,Fmy eye meaning I needed over 39
OL,8,Fappointments and a multitude of
OL,9,Finjections. This was all caused from
OL,10,Fthe stress and upset of the cruel way
OL,11,Fwe lost Linda," he said.
OL,13,F"I want to say that because of the
OL,14,Facts of Mr Hartley, our family have
OL,15,Fstruggled every day since.
OL,17,F"The last four years have been the
OL,18,Fworst of my life because of the
OL,19,Factions Mr Hartley made that night."
